| File | Role |
|---|---|
| `kanban/server/db/queries.js` | All DB logic; `moveCard` to be enhanced; `renormalizeColumn` to be extracted and exported |
| `kanban/server/test/db.test.mjs` | All server-side DB unit tests; new tests added here |

